ni-ša-me-ma ru-ba-um it ru-ba-tum [<gap> ] a-ba-u-ni be-lu-u-ni a-tit-ni be-lu-ni ki-ma ma-tum sa-hi-at-ni a-na ša-ri-ku-nu ni-iš-pu-ra-am ||| We heard that the king and the queen [ <gap> ]. Dear fathers and lords, our lords: since the land was in turmoil, we wrote to you to put you straight.
