na-áš-pè-ra-tim ša A-limki ša En-na-num ub-lá-ku-ni i-hi-id-ma a-ba-tí-qí-im pá-ni-im-ma dí-in-ma lu-ub-lu iš-tí wa-ṣí-im pá-ni-im-ma lu-ṣí-am ||| Pay attention to the missives from the City that Ennanum brought to you, and give it to the very first express transport so they may bring it. He should leave with the first travellers to depart
