3 GÍN KÙ.BABBAR ša 30 TÚG.HI.A iš-tù Ú-lá-ma a-dí Pu-ru-uš-ha-dim ù É wa-áb-ri ||| 3 shekels of silver for the 30 textiles from Ulama to Purušhaddum, including lodgings
i-na Tù-úh-pì-a iṣ-bu-tù-ni-ma 5 ma-na AN.NA áš-qúl ||| In Tuhpiya they seized me and I paid 5 minas of tin
