a-na Ša-lá-tí-wa-ar ha-ra-na-tum lá na-ṭù a-[tù]-ar-ma a-na Ú-la-ma e-li ||| the roads to Šalatuwar are not feasible (to travel), so I will turn around and go up to Ulama
Im-li-kà-a i-na Ú-lá-ma i-na wa-ra-dí-ni iṣ-ba-at-ni-a-tí-ma ||| Imlikaya seized us (as witnesses) in Ulama on our way down (from Kaneš)
