a-na 10-tim ša Té-ga-ra-ma um-ma A-ni-šu-ki-ba ba-ru-lu-um ša Tí-pu-ur-zi-a ||| To the ten-man board of Tegarama from Anišu-kiba, the barullum-official in Tiburziya
