ki-ma ú-ma-sú-hu-šu-nu-ni a-na ma-tim e-ta-áb-tù ||| Because they had been mistreating them, they fled into the countryside
a-sú-ri a-na ma-at Za-al-pá e i-li-ku-ú ||| they are not to go to the Land of Zalpa
