1 1/4 GÍN KÙ.BABBAR a-šu-mì Ha-ha-ma a-na ma-ar-ší i-na Ší-na-hu-tí áš-qú-ul ||| I paid 1 1/4 shekels of silver on behalf of Hahha in Šinahuttum
