a-na kà-ri-im Kà-ni-iš qí-bi-ma um-ma I-ku-pí-a A-du-da ù wa-bar-tum ša Ší-na-hu-tí-ma ||| To the Kaneš Colony from Ikun-piya, Aduda and the Station of Šinahuttum
TÚG.HI a-na 8 1/2 GÍN KÙ.BABBAR ni-il-qí-ma a-na É.GAL-lim ni-ší-ma ||| we took textiles worth 8 1/2 shekels of silver (each) and carried (them) to the palace
