a-šu-mì ša KÙ.BABBAR a-dí u4-mì-im a-nim la ú-šé-bi-<lu>-nim É.GAL-lúm i-na Tù-ha-pí-a ik-la-a-ni-ma 10 u4-me ú-ša-as-hi-ra-ni i-na Wa-ah-šu-ša-na a-li-kam-ma É.GAL-lúm ni-ki-il5-tám iš-ku-ma ú-nu-tí iš-tù ha-ra-nim ú-ta-e-ru-nim-ma a-na Ša-la-tù-ar áp-tù-nu a-na ša-am-ší ša a-na Pu-ru-uš-ha-dim ú-ṣú-ni Sú-en6-pí-lá-ah aṭ-ru-dam ||| Regarding the fact that they have not sent any money until this day – the palace in Tuhapiya held me back and had me delayed for ten days. I came into Wahšušana, but the palace brought about trick, and they returned my goods from the caravan and so I turned toward Šalatuwar. I sent off Su'en-pilah for the day they will leave for Purušhaddum.
a-ma 3 li-mì URUDU ru-ba-um Wa-ah-šu-ša-na-i-um a-na ga-ma-ar-tim e-pu-ul-kà ||| I have completed 3000 talents of copper for the ruler of Wahšušana
