a-na ma-at Wa-ah-šu-š[a-na] mu-uq-ta šu-ma [lá] ta-am-qú-ta iš-tí-ku-nu na-ak-ra-ak ||| Attack the land of Wahšušana. If you do not attack, you are an enemy to us.
