li-ba-ka la i-la-mi-in la li-bi4 DINGIR-ma pi-ri-tum i-li-bi ma-tim i-si-ki-ma a-si-a-ti I ITU u 2 ITU ak-ta-ta a-di ma-tum is-li-mu it ši-ti KU.BABBAR-pi-ku-nu is-ti a-li-ki wa-ar-ki-u-tim u-šie-ba-la-kum ||| Do not be angry. Alas, fear is placed in the heart of the land, and for that reason I have been held back for a couple of months. As soon as the land settles down, I will send the rest of your money with the first travellers (leaving).
