53 ma-na URUDU sa 2 Nib-na-sa-a-a 3 i-se-er Im-lik-a-a 4 Ga-za-a z2 Nu-ih-sa-tim 5 dIM-su-lu-li 6 i-sac is-tat ITU.KAM 7 ab-sa-ra-ni 8 li-mu-um 9 A-gur-i-mì-ti 10 a-na sa-na-at 11 i-sa-qal URUDU i-qa-qa-ad 12 salam-su-<nu> ra-id-is sú-ma la is-qu-ul 13 ki-ma a-wa-at ka-ri-im 14 si-ib-tam u-sa-ab 15 URUDU a-num is-tû 16 30 ma-na URUDU sa-aq-lu 17 a-su-mi Ga-za-a 18 it 53 ma-na URUDU 19 a-su-mi Ga-za-ma 20 Im-lik-a-a 21 qa-ta-tum ||| Adad-sulúli has 53 minas of copper from Ninasa as a claim on Imlikaya, Gaza, and Nuhsatum. (Gaza) will pay within one year from month 5, year eponym Assur-imitti. The obligation to pay back the copper is upon whoever among them is solvent. If he does not pay, he will add interest according to the rate decreed by the karum. This copper is (the amount) after 30 minas had been paid; on behalf of Gaza; and the 53 minas of copper are also on behalf of Gaza; Imlikâya is guarantor.
