dUTU-ŠI-kan mahhan ŠA LUGAL KUR uru dU-tassa ŠA DINGIR.MEŠ uru dU-tassa sahhan luzzi katta ūhhun nℵat dassu ULℵatℵsi tarahhūwas ||| When My Majesty inspected the sahhan (and) luzzi-services of the country of Tarhuntassa to the gods of Tarhuntassa, they were hard and not for him to bear
